Package crm.oilwhere.dto

Class PurchaseDTO

java.lang.Object
crm.oilwhere.dto.PurchaseDTO
public class PurchaseDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object for purchase details. Contains information related to a purchase, including sale date, type, customer details, product details, and pricing information.
